Interface TableChangesJsonParser

public interface TableChangesJsonParser

Implementations of this interface will be responsible for parsing a JSON input stream and sending the events of tables and rows parsed to TableChangesCallback.

Since:
1.0.0

Parses the JSON input stream and sends events of tables and rows parsed to the provided TableChangesCallback.

Parameters:
inputStream - the raw JSON input stream
